I feel creepy.

285
00:18:50,079 --> 00:18:51,280
He's just slow to warm up.

286
00:18:52,079 --> 00:18:53,312
Once you are familiar, it'll be fine.

287
00:18:53,880 --> 00:18:55,000
Actually, he's quite righteous.

288
00:18:56,920 --> 00:18:59,719
