No, two shots, okay?

345
00:21:29,240 --> 00:21:33,159
I don't want to.
I just want to give Li Duo a shot.

346
00:21:33,159 --> 00:21:35,599
Xiaowu, we men should show

347
00:21:35,599 --> 00:21:38,359
